Class QueryResultGenerator

java.lang.Object

              WYSIWYM.transformer.BrowsingGenerator
                  WYSIWYM.transformer.QueryResultGenerator

public class QueryResultGenerator
extends BrowsingGenerator

QueryResultGenerator generates the feedback text of all objects that matched a certain query. This text can be expanded by the user in the same way as a browsing description. There is a separate generator because a QueryResultGraph has >1 root.

Version:
1.4 24-09-2008
Author:
Feikje Hielkema
